{"tid":415502,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"脆香雞翼真係好好食","createTime":"2017-09-27T04:35:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T20:59:53.000Z","uid":46010,"like":1520,"dislike":140,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"c991502b71aa7493fc4545f955f5c081b1bb1906","tid":415502,"uid":46010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T04:35:07.000Z","msg":"講到m記<br />\n脆香雞翼真係冇得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但真係好撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nm記幾時先搞雞翼特價<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位巴絲打食脆香雞翼<br />\n會唔會食埋d軟骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 軟骨先係精華唔食正on9<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 軟骨比狗食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3cb5a659c91335fd052c94ae44a8eab5299413b","tid":415502,"uid":51114,"like":31,"dislike":4,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T04:36:10.000Z","msg":"食雞翼就係為左食軟骨"},{"pid":"d1e7fe028a8292e853eb1277a58936a6fde1e702","tid":415502,"uid":129039,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T04:36:30.000Z","msg":"我食咩雞翼都會連軟骨食 好好咬"},{"pid":"b2982b289cefafa43e1bc08f8b76d9a5a88e2773","tid":415502,"uid":46010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T04:37:47.000Z","msg":"軟骨一方暫時領先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72dc9308a2a6f16c69685e251778120b3e879ec7","tid":415502,"uid":93807,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T04:40:55.000Z","msg":"我連D骨嘅最頭最尾個part都食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 陣骨味好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c7f0a054475668e971d82a48ffa6a6decb3330","tid":415502,"uid":46010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-