f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好邪惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6c725f9343f0d4441643f4b777cc1155aa291b3","tid":415502,"uid":2059,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:10:27.000Z","msg":"先咬一啖炸皮<br />\n再啜+奶炸皮同肉之間既肉汁雞油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再輕輕咁食出面層炸皮<br />\n再食炸皮同肉之間個塊滑嫩既雞皮<br />\n再品嚐雞肉<br />\n最後就食軟骨食到索索性+ 奶乾淨兩條骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原汁原味 唔點醬"},{"pid":"18e601f773adfd860eed53bcafc8fa2bc4029d6d","tid":415502,"uid":61962,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:14:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/sr0px956\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fsr0px956&h=a3886a41&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cec902ef425ff68bb271b222086ea751d47b7cb4","tid":415502,"uid":3172,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:42:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>識叫一定叫全翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n扯左2條骨出黎之後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ebeae5262c2f92229c3fbc9d25ed9a1a041c6fb","tid":415502,"uid":64839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"